<p><b>What is the summary of getting more by Stuart Diamond?</b> Brief summary Getting More by Stuart Diamond is a negotiation guidebook that teaches you how to have successful conversations by focusing on understanding and meeting the other side's needs. It provides practical tips for problem-solving and building stronger relationships.</p>
